15 Saraṇaduka, Cūḷantaraduka
Saraṇaduka, Cūḷantaraduka
46.
149Nasaraṇaṃ naappaccayaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…  nasaraṇaṃ naasaṅkhataṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate pañca.
150Nasaraṇaṃ nasanidassanaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate pañca.
151Nasaraṇaṃ nasappaṭighaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate pañca.
152Nasaraṇaṃ naappaṭighaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā ekaṃ…pe…  avigate ekaṃ.
153Nasaraṇaṃ narūpiṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā dve…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate dve.
154Nasaraṇaṃ naarūpiṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā ekaṃ…pe…  avigate ekaṃ.
155Nasaraṇaṃ nalokiyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ. Sabbattha ekaṃ.)
156Nasaraṇaṃ nalokuttaraṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate pañca.
157Nasaraṇaṃ nakenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca…pe…  nasaraṇaṃ nanakenaci viññeyyaṃ dhammaṃ paṭicca… . (Saṃkhittaṃ.) Hetuyā pañca, ārammaṇe dve…pe…  vipāke ekaṃ…pe…  avigate pañca.
